s across the board are green this week.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's reflected in the industry's total market cap, which is forming its strongest consecutive weekly candles since March.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And things are even better for meme coins.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Popcat has booked an 80% gain this week.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dogwifhat and Pepe are each up over 30%.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepe_the_Frog\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.259363508230575e-15, \"text\": \"Pepe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepe_the_Frog\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepe_the_Frog\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Investors are hungry for crypto gains again, and meme coins are the first call of order.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, all eyes are on the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony will commence on 26 July, and the Paralympics closing ceremony is on 8 September.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Meme Games' presale will roll out through that time frame and debut on exchanges on 10 September.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a setup bound to draw huge interest.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But The Meme Games is not the first crypto to tap into the Olympian enigma.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999799911168, \"rank\": 1.7099137475841613e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\"